name: Magus
description: Emerging from a cocoon, the being known as Adam Warlock defies his creators' intentions and proves to be an important cosmic entity.

name: Aleta Ogord
description: Aleta Ogord is the star-faring Starhawk, a heroine of living light who shares her physical being with Stakar, and a dedicated Guardian of the Galaxy.

name: Warren Kenneth Worthington III
description: One of the original X-Men, the wealthy Warren Worthington III is a mutant with the power of flight and recognized by his angel-like wings.

name: Scott Lang
description: Overcoming his criminal past, Scott Lang follows in the tiny, yet mighty, footsteps of his predecessor as the size-changing hero known as Ant-Man!

name: Sean Cassidy
description: With his sonic scream and Interpol training, Banshee becomes a key member of the X-Men and trains the next generation of mutants.

name: Henry Phillip McCoy
description: A genius scientist and scholar, Beast has a vast intellect to complement his great strength, contributing both to the X-Men and Avengers.

name: Felicia Hardy
description: Black Cat follows in the footsteps of her father learning the tricks of the trade for burglary, eventually losing her criminal ways to fight for the greater good.

name: T'Challa
description: T’Challa is the king of the secretive and highly advanced African nation of Wakanda - as well as the powerful warrior known as the Black Panther.

name: Natasha Romanova
description: Despite super spy Natasha Romanoff’s checkered past, she’s become one of S.H.I.E.L.D.’s most deadly assassins and a frequent member of the Avengers.

name: Eric Brooks
description: Himself a half-human/half-vampire, Daywalker Eric Brooks has honed his abilities to hunt down the undead who have long terrorized mankind.

name: Henry Camp
description: Super Villain Henry Camp is Bulldozer, the head-butting, mystically-empowered human who joins the Wrecking Crew to commit criminal acts.

name: Nathan Summers
description: Sent to the future to survive a deadly infection, the cybernetically enhanced mutant Cable returns to the present and helps the X-Men.

name: Steve Rogers
description: Recipient of the Super Soldier serum, World War II hero Steve Rogers fights for American ideals as one of the world’s mightiest heroes and the leader of the Avengers.
